This Readme  contains list of changes to be made on Banana pi OpenWrt build to be configured 
onewifi test suite external agent.


List of files to be added to Banana pi openwrt build:
----------------------------------------------------
InterfaceMap.json = this json file has wireless interfaces to be configured on Banana pi 
99-lan3_OTS_bringup.sh = lan3 hotplug script for configuring network namespace 
ots_init_file = this file is executed at init, to configure the wireless interface as per 
InterfaceMap.json and start the cci process.
network = this file network configuration for banana pi openwrt build

Changes to be added on openwrt build
------------------------------------
1) mkdir /nvram

2) copy InterfaceMap.json to /nvram directory
$ cp InterfaceMap.json /nvram/.

3) copy the file 99-lan3_OTS_bringup.sh to directory /etc/hotplug.d/iface
$ cp 99-lan3_OTS_bringup.sh /etc/hotplug.d/iface/.
$ chmod +x /etc/hotplug.d/iface/99-lan3_OTS_bringup.sh

4) copy the file ots_init_file to /etc/init.d/.
$ cp ots_init_file /etc/init.d/.
$ chmod +x /etc/init.d/ots_init_file
$ ln -sf /etc/init.d/ots_init_file /etc/rc.d/S99xots_init_file

5) replace /etc/config/network with this network.
$ cp network /etc/config/network
